        FailedAccess other = (FailedAccess) obj;

                return false;

            return false;
        if (resourceId == null) {
            if (other.getResourceId() != null)
                return false;
        } else if (!resourceId.equals(other.getResourceId()))
            return false;
        return true;
    }
